### Frontend Layer

#### [MODIFY] [index.html](file:///c:/Users/justi/Downloads/School%20Files/MainProjectCollection/ComprogStudies/ProjectsWebDev/Capstone Things/DeveloperVersion/frontend/index.html)
- **Roster Online Indicators**: Update `renderStaffManagement` to render a pulsing green dot (`Online`) next to the staff name if their `lastActiveAt` is less than 5 minutes old, otherwise a gray dot (`Offline`).
